Package model

Interface Summary
DownloadDatasetObserver Observer of dataset downloads interface.
DownloadFileObserver Observer of file downloads interface.
 

Class Summary
Dataset Represents a ESGF Dataset of a Output Climate Model.
DatasetDownloadStatus Representation of status of dataset download.
DatasetFile Represents a ESGF File of Output Climate Model Dataset.
Document Represents a document returned by RESTful search.
Facet The Facet class represents ESGF RESTful service facets.
FacetValue Public class that epresents a faced value, with its name and facet value datasets count
FileDownloadStatus Status of a dataset file download.
Keywords The Keyword class represents ESGF RESTful service keywords Keywords parameters are query parameters that have reserved names, and are interpreted by the search service to control the fundamental nature of a search request: where to issue the request to, how many results to return, etc.
RESTful The RESTful class is a abstract class that represents the structure of ESGF RESTful API.
RESTfulSearch The RESTfulSearch class extends RESTful, to implement search functionality.
RESTfulWget The RESTfulSearch class extends RESTful, to implement wget functionality.
 

Enum Summary
ChecksumType Checksum Algorithms
DownloadPriority To specify download priority.
Format To specify the response document output format .
Metadata The Metadata Enum class lists each of the possible metadata defined by ESGF.
RecordStatus To specify download status: created, started, paused, finished and skipped.
SearchCategoryFacet Facets supported by most ESGF Index Nodes in the federation, and can be used to discover/query/retrieve CMIP5 data.
